                  "kind": "text",
                  "data": "Now I have a clear picture. Here's the comparison:\n\n---\n\n## Current Project State vs. Android MVP Spec\n\n### What Exists Now\n\nThe project is essentially an **empty Android Studio template** — the default \"Hello World\" generated by the New Project wizard. Specifically:\n\n| Area | Current State |\n|------|--------------|\n| Source files | 4 Kotlin files: `MainActivity.kt` + 3 theme files (`Color.kt`, `Theme.kt`, `Type.kt`) |\n| Functionality | Displays \"Hello Android\" text. Nothing else. |\n| Architecture | None — no MVVM, no layers, no DI |\n| Package | `com.example.eyecarev2` (spec says `com.eyecare.app`) |\n| Dependencies | Only Compose core + Material 3 + lifecycle |\n| Min SDK | 24 (spec requires 26) |\n| Target SDK | 36 (spec says 35, but 36 is fine/newer) |\n| Theme | Default purple Material 3 with dynamic color enabled (spec wants fixed clinical blue palette, dynamic color OFF) |\n| Typography | Default system fonts (spec wants Outfit + DM Sans) |\n\n### What the Spec Requires (21 Tasks across 7 Phases)\n\n**Phase 1 — Foundation (Tasks 1–4):** ❌ Not started\n- No Hilt DI setup\n- No Retrofit/OkHttp networking\n- No Kotlinx Serialization\n- No EncryptedSharedPreferences / token management\n- No auth interceptor\n- No login/register screens\n- No Navigation Compose / nav graph\n- No bottom navigation bar\n- No auth gate\n- No `BuildConfig.API_BASE_URL`\n- No ktlint configured\n- No version catalog entries for Hilt, Retrofit, Room, Coil, Navigation, etc.\n\n**Phase 2 — Appointments & Home (Tasks 5–7):** ❌ Not started\n\n**Phase 3 — Product Catalog (Tasks 8–10):** ❌ Not started\n\n**Phase 4 — AR Try-On (Tasks 11–12):** ❌ Not started\n\n**Phase 5 — Orders & Billing (Tasks 13–15):** ❌ Not started\n\n**Phase 6 — Prescriptions, Messaging & Feedback (Tasks 16–19):** ❌ Not started\n\n**Phase 7 — Polish & Defense Prep (Tasks 20–21):** ❌ Not started\n\n### Key Gaps Summary\n\n1. **0% of spec implemented.** The project hasn't moved past the Android Studio project creation wizard.\n2. **Wrong package name** — `com.example.eyecarev2` vs spec's `com.eyecare.app`.\n3. **Missing all core dependencies** — Hilt, Retrofit, OkHttp, Room, Kotlinx Serialization, Coil, Navigation Compose, CameraX, MediaPipe, ARCore.\n4. **No project structure** — spec defines `di/`, `data/`, `domain/`, `presentation/` layers; none exist.\n5. **Wrong min SDK** — 24 vs required 26.\n6. **Theme mismatch** — using default purple dynamic colors instead of the fixed clinical blue palette.\n7. **No build flavors** — no `BuildConfig.API_BASE_URL` configuration.\n\n### Where to Start\n\nThe project needs to begin at **Task 1: Project Scaffolding** — setting up Gradle with all dependencies, Hilt, Retrofit, correct package structure, build config fields, and ktlint. Would you like me to start implementing that?"
